    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 unassessed factors are acceptable per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 at this model risk level. CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all 5 operating points with maximum deviation of 14.2% from experimental measurements. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision for this Class II CPB device.",
